headline: GTA Online
subtitle: GTA Online Bonuses and Discounts through November 6th
content:
Take advantage of double GTA$ & RP on Smuggler’s Run Sell Missions, Stockpile and Condemned along with 25% discounts on the following vehicles:

Progen GP1
Western Besra
Nagasaki Blazer Aqua
Grotti Cheetah Classic
HVY Insurgent
Lampadati Toro

And don’t forget, Bodyguard and Associate salaries are paying out double all week long. Check out the Rockstar Newswire for all the details.
